text: Leslie Fu (born November 23, 1992), also known by her online name fuslie, is an American Twitch streamer and Youtubers. She was born in San Francisco, California. She is known for playing Valorant, Among Us, Minecraft and Animal Crossing. ==Early life== Fuslie was born in the San Francisco Bay Area, California on November 23, 1992.
